{
  "dashboard": {
    "id": null,
    "uid": "wilsy-reliability-singularity",
    "title": "🏛️ WILSY OS - Sovereign Reliability [SINGULARITY]",
    "timezone": "browser",
    "refresh": "10s",
    "theme": "dark",
    "schemaVersion": 36,
    "version": 1,
    "panels": [
      {
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Institutional Uptime Ratio (Sovereign Finality)",
        "id": 1,
        "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 8, "h": 6 },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "(1 - (wilsy_counter_system_downtime_seconds{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\"} / wilsy_counter_system_total_time_seconds{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\"})) * 100",
            "legendFormat": "Uptime %"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "decimals": 3,
            "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                { "color": "red", "value": 0 },
                { "color": "#d4af37", "value": 99.9 },
                { "color": "green", "value": 99.999 }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "options": { "colorMode": "background", "justifyMode": "center" }
      },
      {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Failover Trigger Velocity (Sovereign Recovery)",
        "id": 2,
        "gridPos": { "x": 8, "y": 0, "w": 8, "h": 6 },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(wilsy_counter_failover_events_total{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\"}[5m])",
            "legendFormat": "Failovers / Sec"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "short",
            "color": { "fixedColor": "#d4af37", "mode": "fixed" },
            "custom": { "drawStyle": "bars" }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Mean Recovery Time (SLA Restoration ms)",
        "id": 3,
        "gridPos": { "x": 16, "y": 0, "w": 8, "h": 6 },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "wilsy_latency_recovery_time_ms{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\"}",
            "legendFormat": "Restoration Speed"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "ms",
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                { "color": "green", "value": 0 },
                { "color": "#d4af37", "value": 500 },
                { "color": "red", "value": 1000 }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Institutional Error Trends (Fracture Velocity)",
        "id": 4,
        "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 6, "w": 24, "h": 8 },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(wilsy_counter_system_errors_total{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\"}[5m])",
            "legendFormat": "Errors / Sec"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "short",
            "color": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" },
            "custom": { "fillOpacity": 10, "lineInterpolation": "smooth" }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "title": "Reliability Executive Narrative",
        "id": 5,
        "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 14, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "### 🏛️ Resilience Finality Report\nWilsy OS proves **Sovereign Continuity**. The **Uptime Ratio** is maintained at institutional levels ($99.999\\%$), while the **Failover Trigger** panel confirms the agility of the automated re-anchoring protocols. **Recovery Latency** remains within sub-second thresholds, ensuring that even during a system strike, the Citadel heals before the board even notices a fracture."
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
